{"tid":580133,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解書局有D書會用膠套包實, 有D就冇包實任揭任睇?","createTime":"2018-03-04T08:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T17:32:57.000Z","uid":66260,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c821f03528f5aee335bd7f8e422a720bb6accd73","tid":580133,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"發現包實果D大部份都係日本作家, 輕小說/推理小說之類<br />\n其次就係漫畫, 圖集<br />\n某D流行文學(高登連登故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ), 散文就冇包實<br />\n<br />\n一直都唔明, 真係咁驚人會打書釘睇晒成本書?<br />\n漫畫圖集我都明, 但係小說包實晒有乜意思?<br />\n你唔包實比人睇頭幾頁, D人覺得好睇吸引到佢地買返去唔係仲好咩?"},{"pid":"c6acea05804f984b07e6eb0fd401d438b8304c26","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"可能驚畀人揭爛，所以用個膠套包住唔畀人睇"},{"pid":"f41a0f7c8ff006309240b55e32f18ae8f69f8da3","tid":580133,"uid":66260,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c6acea05804f984b07e6eb0fd401d438b8304c26","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"可能驚畀人揭爛，所以用個膠套包住唔畀人睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"其他書又唔驚?<br />\n再唔係擺一本demo比人睇, 其餘照包"},{"pid":"6cff299ebd651e1457a5d4539f270f761a7eb9ae","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f41a0f7c8ff006309240b55e32f18ae8f69f8da3","tid":580133,"uid":66260,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c6acea05804f984b07e6eb0fd401d438b8304c26","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"可能驚畀人揭爛，所以用個膠套包住唔畀人睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"其他書又唔驚?<br />\n再唔係擺一本demo比人睇, 其餘照包"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"因為果啲係暢銷書多人揭？定係裏面既內容唔適合小朋友睇所以包？我都係估估吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDemo 個方法幾好"},{"pid":"0799c0de11374ac39bd6ac462793d62472eadd05","tid":580133,"uid":21558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"我理解係入貨量問題<br />\n日本小說進貨量少 <br />\n多數人見本書揭到肉酸啲都唔肯買<br />\n所以索性包住<br />\n<br />\n本地小說發行量好多固定左一個數<br />\n書店少，變相每間書店分得多貨<br />\n咁就可以唔洗包<br />\n俾啲人任睇"},{"pid":"c0c7321ee949fad81b00109b20bbbdd92bc3ba62","tid":580133,"uid":61954,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"因為包唔包書係出版商既事<br />\n唔關書局事"},{"pid":"98383446eab47fea38e659b62c73702b26523042","tid":580133,"uid":36237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"有時d書擺得耐冇包會好舊好黃咁 包左擺耐d都冇咁舊"},{"pid":"a045e633312c101236a37e9143a179f2c4f84150","tid":580133,"uid":153847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cff299ebd651e1457a5d4539f270f761a7eb9ae","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f41a0f7c8ff006309240b55e32f18ae8f69f8da3","tid":580133,"uid":66260,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c6acea05804f984b07e6eb0fd401d438b8304c26","tid":580133,"uid":130698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"可能驚畀人揭爛，所以用個膠套包住唔畀人睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"其他書又唔驚?<br />\n再唔係擺一本demo比人睇, 其餘照包"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"因為果啲係暢銷書多人揭？定係裏面既內容唔適合小朋友睇所以包？我都係估估吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDemo 個方法幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"誠品好似暢銷書會有demo任揭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得啲練習封住曬，齋睇封底啲描述根本唔知本嘢好唔好<br />\n<br />\n可能驚比人抄題目，但係有啲又冇包"},{"pid":"b554d00ab5e37e56c15703033aabba76955942cb","tid":580133,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得啲外國書有包住係正常，因為冇咁多貨，陣間俾人揭到殘晒又冇貨就大鑊，但有時唔明點解啲練習/參考書都會包實，噉啲人買嗰陣咪淨係可以睇佢書背嘅介紹但唔知入面嘅內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=