e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果冇睇demo,根本唔會買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"我上年12月底去誠品<br />\n誠品連狗年風水書都冇包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘇民峰果本被人揭到彎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6e1b2ae36164df9e50d0e507e98b4bfe3e279d","tid":580133,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:53:27.000Z","msg":"去香港賣日本書嘅鋪頭<br />\n又係全撚部都包實<br />\n淨係睇封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣 <a href=\"http://我不如amazon.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82amazon.jp&d=vxBuxWVO3%2B2ha190jfl7IgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=186d6a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我不如amazon.jp</a>網購<br />\n仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲除咗睇封面 有埋人地評價睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c18afe842f8067b086a29ec429479848b59bbb7","tid":580133,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該有一本開得，其他全部包住，比人搞到殘晒我先唔會買"},{"pid":"2fa18d9c7d4fae58e27badc4b175845d92080b66","tid":580133,"uid":98167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"由出版商返貨既時候已經包好咗<br />\n如果有客要求既話我哋先會拆開<br />\n如果唔係既話會直接上架 唔會遂本拆開哂佢<br />\n當然 仲有其他原因會自己包書<br />\n例如：書皮既質料令封面翹起 18禁 有贈品 過於殘舊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：書店小職員</span></span>"},{"pid":"7706d1283b18836e32570ffff3e6f6b1f486d630","tid":580133,"uid":98167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8fecfc2f74ef78fd9029fa6a088a0e383188a3e8","tid":580133,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4379ca70eba1cd19dfd72fa6cd66d3a02be25a63","tid":580133,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"其實只係因為唔會特登做咁多野<br />\n<br />\n你諗下書店有幾千本書，每本整demo/拆開，要整幾耐？新書一番黎就入架算，通常有demo 都只係暢銷或者有人request"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"即係佢地唔拆純粹係費事煩?<br />\n如果我自己拆會唔會被屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會屌 但如果問一聲感覺會比較好"},{"pid":"00b2b9012ee58504cc4b4289fdaa044c0ada1a62","tid":580133,"uid":769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"好多時會買因為睇睇下覺得岩睇先買返去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}